==經過==
當地時間20時59分，217號班機從列寧格勒機場起飛，約50分鐘後向謝列梅捷沃機場進近。在不良天氣下<ref>{{cite journal|title= Aeroflot accident at Moscow|journal= Flight International|date= 1972-10-19|pages= 517|format= pdf|url= http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1972/1972%20-%202755.html|accessdate= 2014-01-06|quote= In what seems likely to be the world's worst aircraft accident, 168 passengers and eight crew were killed when an Il-62 of Aeroflot crashed on the approach to Moscow, Sheremetyevo, Airport on October 13. The aircraft was on a non-scheduled flight from Paris via Leningrad and it was reported to have crashed while making its approach in bad weather.|archive-date= 2012-11-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121105213856/http://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1972/1972%20-%202755.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>
，機組人員接到下降至400米高度的指示，在降落過程中以620km/h的指示空速和12m/s的垂直速度下降，最終撞地。該事故的可能原因是遭雷擊失控或升降舵故障，但至今仍未查明。<ref name="id=19721013-1">{{cite web|url= http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19721013-1|title= ASN Aircraft accident Ilyushin 62 CCCP-86671 Moskva-Sheremetyevo Airport (SVO)|accessdate= 2014-01-06|archive-date= 2013-04-08|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/6FiTtuFhW?url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19721013-1|dead-url= no}}</ref>

